{"type":"message","id":"c9084cf9","parentId":"2e73487f","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:51:59.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，安装成功了。让我查看一下这个技能的文件结构，了解它提供什么功能，以及配置要求。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"安装成功！`feishu-doc-manager` 已安装到 `/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-doc-manager`。\n\n让我查看一下这个技能的说明和配置要求："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6093787eae9d468b8d0476a1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-doc-manager/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":16571,"output":161,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16732,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773287515540}}
{"type":"message","id":"41de8a1f","parentId":"c9084cf9","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:51:59.758Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6093787eae9d468b8d0476a1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc-manager\ndescription: |\n  📄 Feishu Doc Manager | 飞书文档管理器\n  \n  Seamlessly publish Markdown content to Feishu Docs with automatic formatting.\n  Solves key pain points: Markdown table conversion, permission management, batch writing.\n  \n  将 Markdown 内容无缝发布到飞书文档，自动渲染格式。\n  解决核心痛点：Markdown 表格转换、权限管理、批量写入。\n  \nhomepage: https://github.com/Shuai-DaiDai/feishu-doc-manager\n---\n\n# 📄 Feishu Doc Manager | 飞书文档管理器\n\n> Seamlessly publish Markdown content to Feishu Docs with automatic formatting.\n> \n> 将 Markdown 内容无缝发布到飞书文档，自动渲染格式。\n\n## 🎯 Problems Solved | 解决的痛点\n\n| Problem | Solution | 问题 | 解决方案 |\n|---------|----------|------|----------|\n| **Markdown tables not rendering** | Auto-convert tables to formatted lists | Markdown 表格无法渲染 | 自动转换为格式化列表 |\n| **Permission management complexity** | One-click collaborator management | 权限管理复杂 | 一键协作者管理 |\n| **400 errors on long content** | Auto-split long documents | 长内容 400 错误 | 自动分段写入 |\n| **Inconsistent formatting** | `write`/`append` auto-render Markdown | 格式不一致 | write/append 自动渲染 |\n\n## ✨ Key Features | 核心功能\n\n### 1. 📝 Smart Markdown Publishing | 智能 Markdown 发布\n- **Auto-render**: `write`/`append` actions automatically render Markdown\n- **Table handling**: Tables auto-converted to formatted lists\n- **Syntax support**: Headers, lists, bold, italic, code, quotes\n\n### 2. 🔐 Permission Management | 权限管理\n- Add/remove collaborators\n- Update permission levels (view/edit/full_access)\n- List current permissions\n\n### 3. 📄 Document Operations | 文档操作\n- Create new documents\n- Write full content with Markdown\n- Append to existing documents\n- Update/delete specific blocks\n\n## 🚀 Quick Start | 快速开始\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills\ngit clone https://github.com/Shuai-DaiDai/feishu-doc-manager.git\n```\n\n## 📋 Supported Markdown | 支持的 Markdown\n\n| Markdown | Feishu Result |\n|----------|---------------|\n| `# Title` | Heading 1 |\n| `- Item` | Bullet list |\n| `**bold**` | Bold |\n| `> quote` | Blockquote |\n\n## 🔧 Important Distinctions | 重要区分\n\n**`write`/`append` vs `update_block`**:\n\n| Feature | `write`/`append` | `update_block` |\n|---------|------------------|----------------|\n| Markdown rendering | ✅ Yes | ❌ No (plain text) |\n\n## 📦 Required Permissions | 必需权限\n\n- `docx:document`\n- `docx:document:write_only`\n- `docs:permission.member`\n\n## 📝 License | 许可证\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773287519755}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac2769df","parentId":"41de8a1f","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:52:04.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到了这个技能的说明。现在我需要告诉用户这个技能已经安装成功，以及它的主要功能和配置要求。\n\n根据 SKILL.md，这个技能：\n- 将 Markdown 内容发布到飞书文档\n- 自动处理 Markdown 表格转换\n- 支持权限管理\n- 解决长内容的 400 错误（自动分段）\n- 支持 create/write/append/update/delete 操作\n\n需要配置的权限：\n- docx:document\n- docx:document:write_only\n- docs:permission.member\n\n还需要飞书开放平台的 APP_ID 和 APP_SECRET。\n\n让我总结给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ 安装成功：feishu-doc-manager**\n\n**技能功能：**\n- 智能发布 Markdown 到飞书文档（自动渲染格式）\n- 自动转换表格为格式化列表\n- 权限管理（添加/移除协作者、设置权限级别）\n- 自动分段避免长内容 400 错误\n- 支持 create/write/append/update/delete 文档操作\n\n**需要配置：**\n1. 飞书开放平台创建应用，获取 `APP_ID` 和 `APP_SECRET`\n2. 授予权限：`docx:document`、`docx:document:write_only`、`docs:permission.member`\n3. 技能会自动处理 Markdown 表格转换和格式渲染\n\n**使用方式：**\n- 触发词：发布文档、写飞书文档、添加到飞书文档等\n- 支持 Markdown 语法：标题、列表、粗体、斜体、代码块、引用\n\n需要帮你运行配置向导吗？还是你想直接开始使用？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":17407,"output":543,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17950,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773287519758}}
{"type":"message","id":"153c0831","parentId":"ac2769df","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:54:42.958Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-12 03:54 UTC] 运行配置向导"}],"timestamp":1773287682950}}
